Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.02,0:00:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健全的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.99,0:00:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄宿在健全的精神和
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.22,0:00:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健全的肉体上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.51,0:00:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿拉克妮大人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.71,0:00:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我主子的灵魂反应消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.30,0:02:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 玛嘉 你已经有所觉悟了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.65,0:02:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还用说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.35,0:02:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然死神大人无法继续战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.42,0:02:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就轮到我们出场了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.65,0:02:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿修罗觉醒\N~直到世界尽头?~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.79,0:02:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.06,0:02:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼神吗 如此邪恶的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.09,0:02:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们上吧 椿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.42,0:02:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.96,0:02:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 BLACK STAR 我也要...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.81,0:03:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米佛涅 赶快带着那个矮子离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.10,0:03:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么啊 我才不是矮子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.55,0:03:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的要去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.94,0:03:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该说过吧 本大爷是要超越神的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.25,0:03:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BLACK STAR
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.35,0:03:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KID 那个是...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.48,0:03:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.83,0:03:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是结界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.09,0:03:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.37,0:03:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了治愈在和死神战斗中受伤的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.02,0:03:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙想休眠了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.41,0:03:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会 做那种事的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.27,0:03:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狂气的波长会不断扩散的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙不用战斗就能用狂气支配整个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.67,0:03:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 就不能坐视不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.32,0:03:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丽兹 帕蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.36,0:03:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.69,0:04:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代替父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.77,0:04:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为死神 来维护这个世界的秩序
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.01,0:04:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DEATH THE KID 你要去哪里 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.80,0:04:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有职人跟随 你一个武器独自一人想去做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪开闪开闪开
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.81,0:04:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛嘉 来的真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.49,0:04:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 出了点事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.10,0:05:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分头行动的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.58,0:05:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然会在这种地方重聚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.34,0:05:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这不是正好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.65,0:05:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.09,0:05:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 把灵魂的根基好好的固定住
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.05,0:05:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可掉以轻心 不然马上就会被狂气的波长所支配的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.18,0:05:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不允许出现那种情况
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.37,0:05:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.13,0:05:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候的债
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.61,0:05:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变本加厉的还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.59,0:05:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守护这个世界的秩序
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.85,0:05:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要为父亲报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.43,0:05:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找你算个清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.21,0:05:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能活着回去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.22,0:05:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就再也不怕什么妖怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.83,0:05:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐那样的话就无敌了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.41,0:06:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 帕蒂 不要在世界上最接近无敌的人面前说这种话好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BLACK STAR
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.15,0:06:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我见识一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.99,0:06:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你超越神的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.12,0:06:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 交给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.05,0:06:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备好了吗 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.51,0:06:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那...那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.63,0:06:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和刚才完全面目全非啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.41,0:06:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还变大了好多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.10,0:06:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃掉了阿拉克妮的灵魂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.74,0:06:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外表什么的无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.60,0:06:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我把你大卸八块 鬼神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.81,0:07:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是虫子 有虫子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.69,0:07:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来有虫子混进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.39,0:07:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.73,0:07:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SOUL的演奏开始了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.30,0:07:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's show time~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.42,0:07:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是 两种相斥的力量的共生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.62,0:07:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退魔波长和黑血同时
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.89,0:07:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.68,0:08:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个皮是怎么回事 太硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.31,0:08:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人已经落入我们的节奏 保持住
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.24,0:08:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到没 玛嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.41,0:08:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 没有效果啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.47,0:08:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 你看看周围
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.37,0:08:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.73,0:08:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结界的组织正在不断弱化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.34,0:08:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们正在压制他的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.62,0:08:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.08,0:08:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.68,0:08:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共鸣连锁也很好的发挥了作用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.44,0:08:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样一口气决胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.90,0:08:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.21,0:08:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被遗弃在心中某个角落被遗忘的不安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.15,0:08:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在不断蔓延的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.92,0:08:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是....
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.84,0:09:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加大火力 继续加快节奏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.46,0:09:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SOUL 听到没 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.79,0:09:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 听到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.55,0:09:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们安静的跟着我的节奏就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.67,0:09:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加快节奏 一口气冲上高潮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.22,0:09:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DEATH CONNON
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.19,0:09:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狩猎魔....
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.79,0:10:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SOUL!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.62,0:10:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都结束了 SOUL
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.63,0:10:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界已经是我的了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.96,0:10:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SOUL!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.54,0:10:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人的吧 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.05,0:10:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼神的身体完好无损...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.32,0:10:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手术很成功
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.45,0:10:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心 静养一段时间就会痊愈的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.88,0:10:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.93,0:10:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.36,0:11:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对他说了很过分的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.68,0:11:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说在找回你之前 不再相信他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.59,0:11:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有我在身边 还是让库罗娜受伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.23,0:11:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不但让他被卷入这么痛苦的战斗中 还让他受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.76,0:11:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就直接告诉他好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.35,0:11:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库罗娜还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.69,0:11:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等他醒过来 就把你的感受告诉他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.89,0:11:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库罗娜 没事吧 库罗娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.70,0:11:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须要去....
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.13,0:11:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛嘉的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.87,0:11:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是纠缠不休呢 还要继续吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.00,0:12:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使在被自己人背叛之后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.33,0:12:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死了 他们我自会收拾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.11,0:12:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在那之前要把你干掉再说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.43,0:12:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之后是谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.44,0:12:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还用说吗 当然是阿拉克妮那个老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.18,0:12:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 真让我吃惊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.56,0:12:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底还有多天真
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.19,0:12:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次你又要说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.31,0:12:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿拉克妮已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.99,0:12:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.16,0:12:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了你以外的士兵都在撤退就是证据
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.26,0:12:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿拉克妮之惧已经覆灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.45,0:12:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.29,0:12:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在你打算怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.26,0:12:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上这里就将只剩下死武专的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.34,0:12:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想一个人战斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.49,0:12:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就先放你一马
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.19,0:12:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咬舌头了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.57,0:12:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我记住
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.53,0:13:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会把你干掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.45,0:13:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦拉  连骂人都一成不变呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.60,0:13:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.65,0:13:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 噪音混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.61,0:13:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们之间一定会做个了断的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.97,0:13:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再会了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.64,0:13:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.75,0:13:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼神制造的结界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.81,0:13:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是和DEATH ROOM一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.07,0:13:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从外部无法作用到的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.84,0:13:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.38,0:13:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狂气的扩散越来越严重
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.24,0:13:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明已经启动了死之城
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.38,0:13:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终究还是无法战胜鬼神吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.99,0:13:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢货 你没长眼睛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.94,0:13:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明自己长了一对圆珠眼睛 还好意思说我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.98,0:13:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有希望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.22,0:13:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.86,0:13:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在结界封闭之前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.69,0:14:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经确认有DEATH THE KID
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.83,0:14:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BLACK STAR 玛嘉·阿尔巴姆3人成功突入
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.12,0:14:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗还没有结束
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.91,0:14:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛嘉他们在里面?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.55,0:14:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然可能性很低 但是只要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.49,0:14:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛嘉阿尔巴姆的退魔波长能...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.86,0:14:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 要是能顺利发挥出力量的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.57,0:14:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定就能打倒鬼神
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.53,0:14:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说都是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.15,0:14:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在只能静静的等待了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.60,0:14:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SOUL SOUL SOUL
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.99,0:14:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 SOUL出什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.30,0:14:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,具体情况我也不知道 但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.62,0:14:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他用力过度了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.13,0:14:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.25,0:14:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼神不见了...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.53,0:14:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贪图一时的后果
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.14,0:15:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,持续使用超出自己能力范围的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.36,0:15:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于付出了代价
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.45,0:15:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说到了偿还代价的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.21,0:15:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说是因为使用黑血的原因吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.60,0:15:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在只有把自己交给狂气才能得到的力量上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.92,0:15:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使套上了名为理性的枷锁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.66,0:15:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之后也必定会出现漏洞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.71,0:15:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将自己完全交给狂气不就好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.69,0:15:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话就不会有什么恐惧的了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.07,0:15:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个混蛋 在那里自言自语个什么劲儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.98,0:15:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别急 不要受他的挑衅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.07,0:15:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没必要跟着对手的节奏走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.67,0:15:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑 自始至终都是按照本大爷的风格来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.58,0:15:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少给我用那些无聊的小伎俩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.47,0:15:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害 用气势就把幻觉给驱走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.11,0:15:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是BLACK STAR
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.69,0:16:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是还是很糟糕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.72,0:16:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共鸣连锁的关键环节SOUL现在是那个状态
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.44,0:16:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KID 援护援护
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.63,0:16:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.58,0:16:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像完全不起作用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.77,0:16:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在鬼神开始反击之前必须找到突破口
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.55,0:16:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不然我们必败无疑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.91,0:16:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脉搏变弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.72,0:16:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也开始面无血色了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.49,0:16:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.05,0:16:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SOUL 我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.14,0:16:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么 玛嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.82,0:16:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.25,0:16:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在能救SOUL的只有玛嘉你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.19,0:16:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点去把那个笨蛋带回来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.32,0:17:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BLACK STAR KID
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.49,0:17:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们说好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.95,0:17:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前 我们一定想办法压制住鬼神
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.55,0:17:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了 你回来的时候就已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.06,0:17:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遗憾呢 玛嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.08,0:17:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看不到我超越神的一瞬间了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.93,0:17:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的 已经太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.93,0:17:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少废话 那可不是你说的算的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.71,0:17:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的对手可是本大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.71,0:17:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 二位
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.95,0:17:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SOUL 我现在就来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.77,0:17:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很微弱 但是还能感觉到SOUL的波长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.99,0:17:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.72,0:18:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.15,0:18:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是?钢琴的演奏?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.02,0:18:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SOUL
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.30,0:20:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在等你 玛嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.78,0:20:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SOUL
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.78,0:20:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是我 玛嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.12,0:20:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BLACK STAR
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.79,0:20:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了 你们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.81,0:21:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.00,0:21:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会让你碰他们两个的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.56,0:21:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们和玛嘉是那么约定的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.66,0:21:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约定就一定要遵守
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.44,0:21:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我们死武专的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.53,0:21:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼神阿修罗 来做个了断吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.02,0:23:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧 椿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.17,0:23:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是我们大显身手的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.02,0:23:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大显身手?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.92,0:23:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 椿 好像没什么精神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.31,0:23:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前就一直在想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.29,0:23:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机会难得 可以说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.27,0:23:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 倒是无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.13,0:23:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们变身武器的时候 台词是不是太少了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.35,0:23:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 SOUL EATER 第50话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.17,0:23:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听天由命 超越神的男子汉们?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.92,0:23:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想再多说点话啊


